        <strong>B.Tech in Computer Science</strong>
        <br/>
        University Name - 2017-2021
        <br/>
        Focus: Algorithms, Distributed Systems, Database Management
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="man-section">
      <h2>METRICS</h2>
      <pre class="metrics-display">
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Performance Stats                           │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤
